cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with text categorization and uses deep learning techniques such as LSTM and CNN. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Computer Vision (cs.CV). Among these, cs.CL is the most likely category as the paper deals with text processing and classification.
